name: homi
description: Homi is an innovative web and mobile application designed to assist new and prospective homeowners in finding their ideal neighborhoods across America. By utilizing advanced AI algorithms, Homi curates personalized neighborhood recommendations based on users' unique preferences and lifestyle factors. Whether you're single, married, or have a family, Homi aims to simplify the home-buying process by connecting users with tailored options that align with their values and aspirations.
